@ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5231

### Đăng ký Sinh viên
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Nguyen Van A",
  "email": "student@example.com",
  "password": "Password1!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password1!",
  "userType": 0
}

### Đăng ký Chủ quán (Business)
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Tran Thi B",
  "email": "business@example.com",
  "password": "Password1!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password1!",
  "userType": 1
}

### Đăng nhập
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "business@example.com",
  "password": "Password1!"
}

### Thông tin tài khoản (cần Bearer token)
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Danh sách gói dịch vụ
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/subscriptions

### Gói hiện tại
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/subscriptions/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Nâng cấp Enterprise (Business)
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/subscriptions/upgrade
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Tính năng Enterprise-only
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/subscriptions/enterprise-features
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
